subject: Tennis
Sporting Goods and Equipment
United States Open (Tennis)
organizations: Billie Jean King National Tennis Center
lead_paragraph: Woody Schneider owns tennis racket shops in Manhattan, but he also runs the National Tennis Center Pro Shop on a year-to-year contract, which stipulates that he has to empty out the shop during the United States Open.
